USAGE PHILOSOPHY:
I frequently receive inquiries about using this codebase, and I'm always happy 
to see developers building upon my work. The answer is yes, with proper attribution.

I'm committed to open source principles while respecting intellectual effort. 
This project represents significant time and creativity, and I'm proud to share it 
with the community.

My only request is simple: acknowledge the original work and don't present it as 
entirely your own creation. A link back and proper credit supports the open source ecosystem.

